	(text "Power budget (matches firmware/doc/chip_design.md §6 = 7.6 W board total)\n  +3V3 : 0.66 W (STM32F4 + ancillaries)\n  +5V  : 0.49 W (LTC2378 + AD5660)\n  +15V : 2.4 W  (AD8429 ×4 + ISO224 ×4)\n  -15V : 1.5 W  (mirror of +15V)\n  +24V_GATE: 1.2 W (TLP358 + IGBT gate)\n  +1V0 (FPGA core): 1.33 W (MMR onboard core LDO)\n  ──────────────────────────────\n  TOTAL: 7.58 W (5%-margined: 8 W power supply)"
